text: "Who Dat B" is a song recorded by American rapper Jessi. It was released on September 23, 2019. The single was her first release since "Down" in 2018, as well as her first release since moving to Psy's P Nation label. It was later part of the EP Nuna which was released on July 30, 2020. == Background and release == On September 16, P Nation announced that Jessi would be releasing a new single on September 23. P Nation had previously posted a photo of Jessi on Instagram account with the hashtag "Spoiler." A source later from the agency stated, "As much as people have been waiting for Jessi's comeback, she has created a single of the utmost quality, and we hope people will be excited to see a new side of Jessi." The first and second teasers were released on September 19, the third and fourth teasers were released on September 20, and the last teaser were released on September 21. The single was released on September 23, 2019 with the release of the music video on YouTube at the same time, directed by korilo (August Frogs). == Promotion == Before the single being released, Jessi held her countdown livestream on Naver's V Live to discuss about her comeback. === Live performance === Jessi performde in JTBC's Lululala Music on September 25, KBS's KBS Kpop on September 27. ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" |- !
